snippet: In a game of cat and mouse, no one appears willing to build a stadium in Los Angeles until a team has committed to moving there.
abstract: Prospect of NFL team moving to Los Angeles for 2015 season is increasingly unlikely as city has yet to find site for new stadium.
lead_paragraph: In a game of cat and mouse, no one appears willing to build a stadium in Los Angeles until a team has committed to moving there.

headline.main: With No Stadium on Horizon, Chances Dim for a Move to Los Angeles in 2015
headline.print_headline: With No Stadium on Horizon, Chances Dim for a Move to Los Angeles in 2015
